tid":1855329,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ijbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=5402ae76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6371c058f1077871478017cd5a0925eace68a9cd","tid":1855329,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多人香港開工番大陸住.日日來回<br />\n不如借呢次cut走埋呢班假香港人</span>"}]}